cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB port for S1U to 0 (out of range) will cause routing failure and prevent proper S1U interface connection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the DL absolute frequency point A to 0 (out of range) will cause frequency misalignment and lead to downlink transmission failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 DL 絕對頻率點 A 設定為 0（超出範圍）會導致頻率錯位，並造成下行鏈路傳輸失敗。
